NG0605:1: shri ha ya gr-i ba tan tra ya de na ma //
NG0605:3: dpal rta mgrin gyi rgyud phyi ma zhes bya ba //
NG0605:4: bcom ldan 'das rta mgrin dbang gi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0605:5: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na //
NG0605:6: bcom ldan 'das pad+ma rigs kyi sangs rgyas shin tu rnam par dag pa //
NG0605:7: pad+ma rigs kyi pho brang rgya khyon dpag tu med pa na //
NG0605:8: 'khor spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la sogs pa //
NG0605:9: byang chub sems dpa' tshogs dang khro bo dang *//
NG0605:12: yang sprul gyi lha tshogs dpag tu med pa rnams dang thabs gcig tu bzhugs so //
NG0605:13: de'i tshe pad+ma gsung gi dbang phyug gis //
NG0605:14: pad+ma rigs kyi sangs rgyas la //
NG0605:15: phyag btsal bskor ba byas nas ni //
NG0605:16: e ma ho sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das //
NG0605:17: pad+ma dbang gi rgyud chen po //
NG0605:18: bsnyen sgrub la sogs bcas pa rnams //
NG0605:19: bdag cag rnams la bshad du gsol //
NG0605:21: de nas bcom ldan 'das pad+ma rigs kyi sangs rgyas kyis //
NG0605:22: khams gsum dbang du sdud pa'i ting nge 'dzin la zhugs pa @#//
NG0605:24: dpal rta mgrin yum gsang ba'i ye shes dang *//
NG0605:25: sras pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug dang *//
NG0605:26: sras mo pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug ma zhes bya ba dang *//
NG0605:27: yab yum sras dang bcas pa bzhengs nas //
NG0605:28: dbang gi rta skad thengs gsum gyis khams gsum dbang du bsdus //
NG0605:29: srid gsum zil gyis mnan nas dregs pa can thams cad tshar bcad par gyur to //
NG0605:30: rta mgrin dregs pa tshar gcod kyi rgyud las //
NG0605:31: gleng gzhi'i le'u ste dang po'o //     // de nas pad+ma rigs kyi sangs rgyas le //
NG0605:32: gsung gi dbang phyug gis 'di skad ces zhus so //
NG0605:33: dbang chen lha bzhi'i bsgrub pa la //
NG0605:34: dang po bsnyen pa ji lta bya //
NG0605:35: de skad gsol ba gsan nas kyang *//
NG0605:36: pad+ma rigs kyi sangs rgyas bka' stsal pa //
NG0605:37: dad dang snying rje brtson 'grus can //
NG0605:39: dben zhing yid 'ong nyams dga' bar //
NG0605:40: sa bdag klu gnyan zhi bya'i phyir //
NG0605:41: mchod sbyin gtor ma rgyas par btang *//
NG0605:42: bkra shis legs pa'i sa blangs la //
NG0605:43: man+dal zla gam gru bzhi bya //
NG0605:44: dri sna'i skyang nul legs byas la //
NG0605:45: me tog dmar po'i tshom bu dgram //
NG0605:46: rta mgrin sku gsung thugs kyi rten //
NG0605:47: mchod rdzas phyi nang bshams nas ni //
NG0605:48: bde ba'i sten la 'dug byas nas //
NG0605:49: thog mar byang chub sems bskyed la //
NG0605:50: rten la tshogs sogs mchod par bya //
NG0605:51: tshad med rnam bzhi sngon btang la //
NG0605:52: skad cig stong ba'i ngang las kyang *//
NG0605:53: rta mgrin sku ru gsal byas la //
NG0605:54: thugs kha nyi dal hrihbsam la //
NG0605:57: phyogs mtshams rdo rje'i rtsig pa la //
NG0605:58: steng 'og rdo rje'i gur dang sa //
NG0605:59: srid pa'i rlung gis mi thar sgom //
NG0605:60: phyi rim bskal ba'i me ri sgom //
NG0605:62: de nas thugs ka'i hri las ni //
NG0605:63: yi ge smug nag brum 'phros pas //
NG0605:64: rin chen sna lnga gzhal yas khang *//
NG0605:65: sgo bzhi rgyan dang bcas par sgom //
NG0605:66: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs su //
NG0605:68: bde gshegs mchod cing 'gro don bya //
NG0605:69: tshur 'dus gser gyi rdo rjer gyur //
NG0605:71: bdag nyid rta mgrin skur bsgoms te //
NG0605:72: sku mdog dmar po bye ru 'dra //
NG0605:73: zhal gcig pa la phyag bzhi pa //
NG0605:74: dbu gtsug rta mgo ljang zhu 'tsher //
NG0605:75: g.yas g.yon dang po yum la 'khyud //
NG0605:76: dbang sdud phyag rgya gdengs pa'o //
NG0605:77: g.yas g.yon rdo rje pad+ma bsnams //
NG0605:78: dbu rgyan rin chen rigs lngas brgyan //
NG0605:79: sbrul dang thod pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NG0605:80: zhabs bzhi nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan //
NG0605:81: gsang ba ye shes mkha' 'gro ma //
NG0605:82: dmar mo zhal gcig phyag bzhi ma //
NG0605:83: g.yas g.yon dang po yab la 'khyud //
NG0605:84: g.yas kyi 'og ma gri gug la //
NG0605:85: g.yon gyi 'og ma thod khrag stob //
NG0605:86: zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum yab la 'khril //
NG0605:88: pa'i rgyan drug sku la brgyan //
NG0605:89: yab yum gnyis kyi zhabs 'og na //
NG0605:91: yab yum gnyis med dbu gtsug na //
NG0605:92: sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas ni //
NG0605:93: sprul sku mnyam gzhag sku mdog dmar //
NG0605:94: rigs kyi bdag pos rgyas gdab sgom //
NG0605:95: thugs khar 'jig rten dbang phyug ni //
NG0605:97: ye shes sems dpa'i tshul du sgom //
NG0605:98: de nas yab kyi thugs ka nas //
NG0605:99: hu~m dmar g.yas phyogs 'phros pa la //
NG0605:100: pad+ma gar dbang sku mdog dmar //
NG0605:101: g.yas g.yon rdo rje pad+ma bsnams //
NG0605:102: zhabs gnyis nyi zla pad+ma la'o //
NG0605:103: yum gyi thugs kha'i hu~m las g.yon //
NG0605:104: pad+ma gar gyi dbang mo yum //
NG0605:105: g.yas pa gri khug g.yon thod pa //
NG0605:107: yab yum bzhi yi skur sgom la //
NG0605:108: khams gsum dbang du sdud pa dang *//
NG0605:109: srid gsum zil gyis gnon pa dang *//
NG0605:110: srid gsum las la 'khor ba bsgom //
NG0605:111: de nas ye shes lha bzhi pa'o //
NG0605:112: 'og min gnas nas spyan drangs la //
NG0605:113: gnyis su med par gzhug cing bstim //
NG0605:114: phyag 'tshal mchod cing bstod pa bya //
NG0605:115: de nas bsnyen pa 'bul ba ni //
NG0605:117: dbu gtsug snang ba mtha' yas kyi //
NG0605:120: thugs ka'i spyan ras gzigs dbang gi //
NG0605:122: om pad+ma ta kri da hu~m //
NG0605:123: sku yi snying po 'bru drug pa //
NG0605:124: om ha ya gr-i ba hu~m //
NG0605:125: gsung gi snying po 'bru drug pa'o //
NG0605:126: om ma ha kro d+ha hu~m /
NG0605:127: thugs kyi snying po 'bru drug pa'o //
NG0605:128: om ha ri ni sa hu~m //
NG0605:129: yum mkha' 'gro'i snying po 'bru drug pa'o /
NG0605:130: yab yum bzhi yi thugs ka nas //
NG0605:132: phyogs bcu'i bde bar gshegs pa la //
NG0605:133: sngags kyi 'od zer phog pa yis //
NG0605:134: sku gsung thugs la mnyes mchod 'bul //
NG0605:135: khams gsum 'gro drug sems can la //
NG0605:136: 'od zer phog pas sgrib pa sbyangs //
NG0605:137: pad+ma dbang gi lhar gyur nas //
NG0605:138: kun kyang rang sngags sgrogs par sgom //
NG0605:139: dus kyi bsnyen pa zhag zla lo //
NG0605:140: ji tsam 'grub par bsgrub par bya //
NG0605:141: grangs kyi bsnyen pa brgya stong khri //
NG0605:142: ji tsam 'grub dang dam bcar bzung *//
NG0605:143: mtshan ma 'grub pa lta yi rtags //
NG0605:144: sku rtags 'od dkar nyams dga' dang *//
NG0605:145: gsung rtags sgra snyan sgrog pa dang *//
NG0605:146: thugs rtags dri zhim 'byung ba dang *//
NG0605:147: sku rtags lha yi zhal ston dang *//
NG0605:148: gsung rtags lung ston chos 'chad dang *//
NG0605:149: thugs rtags chos nyid rtogs par 'char //
NG0605:150: sku rtags lus kyi nad sos dang *//
NG0605:151: gsung rtags ngag la nus pa 'byung *//
NG0605:152: thugs rtags dug lnga khong du song *//
NG0605:153: de ltar rtags rnams thon par sgrub //
NG0605:155: rta mgrin dregs pa tshar gcod kyi rgyud las //
NG0605:156: bsnyen pa'i skabs te dang po'o //  // de nas yang dag bshad bya ba //
NG0605:159: dkyil 'khor mtha' dgang gru bzhi la //
NG0605:160: chag chag skyang nul legs byas la //
NG0605:161: gzhung bzhin legs par thig btab ste //
NG0605:162: dkyil 'khor dbus su zla gam la //
NG0605:163: mu khyud zla kham dmar po 'od zer 'phro //
NG0605:164: gru chad sgro bzhi phyogs dang bcas //
NG0605:165: sgo rgyan mu khyud rdo rje me ris bskor //
NG0605:166: dbus su mtshan ldan dum bu bzhi pa ru //
NG0605:167: pad+ma mtshan dang khrag bsres la //
NG0605:168: mtha' ma zhi khro'i sngags kyis bskor //
NG0605:169: nang du sman dang rin chen dang *//
NG0605:170: 'bru sna lnga la sogs pa blug / dngos grub
NG0605:171: ci 'dod gsol byang gzhug / le rgan dar du
NG0605:172: dril nas ni // dkyil 'khor dbus su stegs la bzhag / gtor ma rak+sha bdud rtsi dang *//
NG0605:173: mchod rdzas rgyas par bshams nas ni //
NG0605:174: tshogs dang dngos grub ci 'dod gsol //
NG0605:175: 'byor pa'i yo byad ci phyir dgram //
NG0605:176: de nas bsrung ba'i 'khor lo dang *//
NG0605:177: ting nge 'dzin gyi lha sgom dang *//
NG0605:178: ye shes dkyil 'khor mchod pa dang *//
NG0605:179: bstod pa la sogs byas nas ni /
NG0605:180: bzlas pas ting 'dzin sngags bstan pa //
NG0605:184: om ha ya gri ba hu~m //
NG0605:186: om ha ri ni sa hu~m //
NG0605:187: om du ma ga ye na ma swaha /
NG0605:188: zhais bzlas pas bdag nyid rta mgrin thugs ka nas //
NG0605:190: spyan tsug snang ba mtha' yas la //
NG0605:191: 'od kyi thugs dam rgyud kyang bskul //
NG0605:192: snang ba mtha' yas thugs ka nas //
NG0605:193: thugs rje chen po'i thugs khar spros //
NG0605:194: thugs dam rgyud bskul mnyes byas nas //
NG0605:195: thugs rje chen po'i thugs kha nas //
NG0605:196: dpa' bo rta mgrin thugs khar phog / rta mgrin thugs dam rgyud bskul nas //
NG0605:197: gsang ba ye shes thugs khar phog / yum gyi thugs dam rgyud bskul nas //
NG0605:199: mkha' 'gro rnam bzhi'i thugs ka nas //
NG0605:201: mi dang lha dang mkha' 'gro dang *//
NG0605:202: zas dang sman dang nor dang 'bru //
NG0605:203: stong gsum thams cad bcud bsdus nas //
NG0605:204: thod pa'i nang du gang bar sgom *//
NG0605:205: 'od dang du ba'i re rnyed dang *//
NG0605:206: ro zhim mang du 'phel ba dang *//
NG0605:207: rmi lam nor dang zas rnyed dag / mi mang zas nor 'bul ba dang *//
NG0605:208: mi mang phyag 'tshal bsnyen bkur byed //
NG0605:209: kun gyi gtso bor dbang bskur dang *//
NG0605:210: glu bro gar gyi sna 'dren dang *//
NG0605:211: chos gter rnyed dang nor rnyed dang *//
NG0605:212: rtags thon dngos grub blang bar bya //
NG0605:213: rtsa sngags rnams kyi mjug la ni //
NG0605:217: dngos grub ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin //
NG0605:218: lha rnams kyis ni gsol bar sgom //
NG0605:219: dngos grub rdzas la phud spros la //
NG0605:220: ye shes lha rnams mchod par bya //
NG0605:221: de nas rang dang sgrub grogs bza' //
NG0605:222: thod par dngos grub rdzas lhag bcad //
NG0605:223: rang dang mi 'brel rtag tu bcang *//
NG0605:225: [(]24[)]@#// phyis kyis sgrub pa'i rten rdzas bya //
NG0605:226: mi la mi bstan spa bar bya //
NG0605:227: rgyun du mkha' 'gro'i snying po bzlas //
NG0605:228: bdag nyid rta mgrin yab yum gyi //
NG0605:230: 'gro ba dbang du sdud pas sgom //
NG0605:233: sgrub pa'i skabs te gnyis pa'o //  // de nas bzlas sbyor bshad par bya //
NG0605:234: drag sngags dregs pa 'dul ba ni *//
NG0605:235: om pad+mam ta kri ha ya gri ba hu lu hu lu hu~m phat //
NG0605:236: rta mgrin dregs pa tshar gcod sngags //
NG0605:238: gshin rje tshar bcad yig 'bru lnga //
NG0605:240: rgyal po tshar gcod yig 'bru lnga //
NG0605:244: btsan gyi tshar gcod yig 'bru lnga //
NG0605:246: lha yi tshar gcod yi ge 'bru lnga //
NG0605:247: a se la stam pa ya /
NG0605:248: sman gyi tshar gcod yig 'bru lnga //
NG0605:250: bdud kyi char gcod yig 'bru lnga //
NG0605:252: srin po tshar gcod yi ge 'bru lnga //
NG0605:254: gnod sbyin tshar gcod yig 'bru lnga //
NG0605:258: dmu yi tshar gcod yig 'bru lnga //
NG0605:260: mu stegs tshar gcod yig 'bru lnga //
NG0605:262: dam sri tshar gcod yig 'bru lnga //
NG0605:263: na ga stam pa yaklu gdon tshar gcod yig 'bru lnga /
NG0605:265: gza' rnams tshar gcod yig 'bru lnga //
NG0605:271: mo 'dre gnod byed tshar gcod yig 'bru lnga //
NG0605:273: yi dgas shin 'dre tshar gcod yig 'bru lnga //
NG0605:275: gnod bgegs thams cad yi ge lnga //
NG0605:281: dregs pa thams cad tshar gcod sngags //
NG0605:290: dgos kyi 'dul na rtsa sngags la //
NG0605:291: so so'i srog snying sham bu sngags //
NG0605:292: bsres la bzlas shing tshar gcad bya //
NG0605:293: spyiru thams cad tshar gcod dril //
NG0605:294: srid pa'i lha 'dre thams cad kun //
NG0605:295: dbang du 'dus nas bka' nyan dang *//
NG0605:296: tshar gcod brlag par the tshom med //
NG0605:298: gnod byed gdon bgeg tshar gcod pa'i skabs te gsum
NG0605:299: pa'o // // de nas las sbyor bshad pa ni
NG0605:300: // bsad pa 'brupa khung las sbyor ni //
NG0605:301: 'brub khung nang du ling ka gzhug / seng ldeng phur pa khro bor bsam //
NG0605:302: sha trum a mu kha ma ra ya hu~m phatasod //
NG0605:303: phur pa gdab cing thun kyang bra ba //
NG0605:304: gang la bya ba brlag par 'gyur //
NG0605:305: sbyin sreg me yi las sbyor ni //
NG0605:306: thab khung dmar nag gru gsum du //
NG0605:307: gdug pa can gyi shing brtsigs la //
NG0605:310: me nang rta mgrin bskyed byas la //
NG0605:311: sbar dkar gtor ma sha khrag mchod pa 'bul //
NG0605:312: dz+wa la ram dz+wa la ram //
NG0605:315: rtsa sngags sbrel la sbyin sreg bya //
NG0605:316: thal ba bskul la mnan gtor bya //
NG0605:317: gtor srang rlung gi las sbyor ni //
NG0605:318: sbyin sreg thal ba nya bo bya //
NG0605:319: snying khar ming rus bcu pa la //
NG0605:320: rlung tshubs ma yis thun du brab //
NG0605:321: brag sgra rlung sgra can du mnan //
NG0605:322: yang na btags la rlung la phyar //
NG0605:323: che ge mo ka ma rag sha ya ra na //
NG0605:324: u tsa ta ya phat phat /
NG0605:325: tsa sngags sbrel la bzlas pa bya //
NG0605:326: dgra bgegs gang byas bskrad par 'gyur //
NG0605:327: mnan pa sa yi las sbyor ni /
NG0605:328: kho yi zag pa'i rdzas btsal la //
NG0605:329: sa nag bsres la nya bo bya //
NG0605:330: ming rus bris la ling khar gzhug / snying khar phur bu btab nas ni //
NG0605:331: thod pa mtshan ngan nang du gzhug / re bas dril la mkhar nag dkri //
NG0605:332: lha khang them 'og rgya gram lam //
NG0605:333: mchod rten snying po'i nang du mnan //
NG0605:334: che ge mo a mu kam /
NG0605:337: ro g.yas rdo rje rgya gram dang *//
NG0605:338: tsha tsha sa tshon rnam lnga mnan //
NG0605:339: lcags kyi khar sgrom 'bar ba nas //
NG0605:340: bskal pa'i mthar yang mi thar bsam //
NG0605:341: dgra bgegs gang yang gnon par 'gyur //
NG0605:342: sbyong byed chu yi 'khor lo ni /
NG0605:343: kham pa rdol byas pa yis //
NG0605:344: gru gsum ga'u kha sbyor du //
NG0605:345: chu 'gram sa la gzugs byas la //
NG0605:346: snying khar gru gsum ming rus gzhug / gang tsher bcug la la chas bsngam //
NG0605:347: bam ni ma ra ya sod sod /
NG0605:348: bam ni ma ra ya thum ril /
NG0605:350: mtsho 'am chu mig chu gzhung bskyur //
NG0605:351: dgra bgegs gang yin rtsa ba 'chad //
NG0605:352: zlog pa zor gyi las sbyor ni *//
NG0605:353: thod pa mtshan ngan nang du ni //
NG0605:354: khrag sna dug sna zangs lcags rdo //
NG0605:355: yungs kar yungs nag ske tshe dang *//
NG0605:356: de la sngags la thun du brab //
NG0605:357: sbod gtong gtong ba'i rkang rjes sa //
NG0605:358: mchil snabs dang ni dri chen chu //
NG0605:359: snying khar mchog phur btab byas na //
NG0605:360: ban d+he sha ya ban d+he sha ya /
NG0605:361: che ge mo ha ha stam ba ya bzlog bzlog
NG0605:362: / sha tram a mu kha ma ra ya bzlos
NG0605:363: sod // thod pa mtshan ngan nya bo bcas //
NG0605:364: rang gi mal 'og mnan par bya //
NG0605:365: thun rdzas dgra yi phyogs su 'phang *//
NG0605:366: phur kha sbod gtong kho la bzlog / bsrung ba'i 'khoralo'i las sbyor ni //
NG0605:367: gro ga'am ni shog bu la //
NG0605:368: gur kum g+hi hang mtshal gyis bri //
NG0605:369: dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs drug la //
NG0605:371: dbus su rta mgrin sku yi sngags //
NG0605:372: rtsibs drug la ni gsung gi sngags //
NG0605:373: rtsibs mchan drug la thugs kyi sngags //
NG0605:374: phyi rol pad+ma yum gyi sngags //
NG0605:375: phyi rol thugs rje chen po'i sngags //
NG0605:376: phyi rol snang ba mtha' yas sngags //
NG0605:377: phyi rol rta mgrin yab yum sngags //
NG0605:378: 'khor lo rab gnas byin brlabs bya //
NG0605:379: la char dpung pa g.yon par gdags //
NG0605:382: nad dang gnod dang bar chad thul //
NG0605:383: dgra bgegs brdung ba'i las sbyor ni //
NG0605:384: rdo rje dmar po rtse lnga pa //
NG0605:385: rta mgrin sngags kyis byin brlabs la //
NG0605:386: sa la dgra bgegs gzugs bris la //
NG0605:387: yang na lcags kyi tho bas brdungs //
NG0605:388: yang na rdo rje tho bas brdungs //
NG0605:389: lo ka log tri sa la tri phung *//
NG0605:394: gam gu ru a be sha ya a be sha ya /
NG0605:395: dgra bgegs gnod byed thum ri li li /
NG0605:397: gnod byed rdul du brlag par 'gyur /
NG0605:398: gdab pa phur pa'i las sbyor ni //
NG0605:399: zangs sam 'khar ba'i phur pa la //
NG0605:400: seng ldeng phur pa khru gang pa //
NG0605:401: rta mgrin skur bskyed dbang bskur la //
NG0605:402: rang dang mi 'bral sngas su gzhug / sri'u nad pa la sogs pa //
NG0605:403: lngas su bsrung ba byas pa ni //
NG0605:404: om pad+ma kro d+ha ha ya grib hu lu hu lu pad+ma ki li ki la ya hu~m phat //
NG0605:405: ces pa bzlas pa byas la byin gyis brlab par bya //
NG0605:406: bgegs la gdengs pa tsam gyis chog / las kyi sbyor ba de rnams la //
NG0605:407: rtsa sngags grub par rab tu gces //
NG0605:408: bdag nyid rta mgrin skur bsgoms la //
NG0605:409: 'jig rten dregs pa dbang du bsdus //
NG0605:410: gang la bya ba gzir byas la //
NG0605:411: gnod bgegs thams cad bsrungs nas 'byin //
NG0605:413: rta mgrin dregs pa tshar gcod kyi rgyud las //
NG0605:414: 'phrin las las sbyor gyi skabs te bzhi pa'o //  // de nas pad+ma rigs kyi sangs rgyas la //
NG0605:415: pad+ma gsung gi dbang phyug gis 'di skad ces bstod do //
NG0605:416: chos sku skye med ngang las ma g.yos par //
NG0605:417: gzugs sku longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur bstan nas //
NG0605:418: sbrul sku dregs pa 'joms mdzad rgyud bshad pa //
NG0605:419: ngo mtshar sangs rgyas khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0605:421: de nas pad+ma sangs rgyas kyis //
NG0605:422: 'khor rnams kun la rgyud bshad pas //
NG0605:423: rta mchog rgyal po'i rgyud 'di ni //
NG0605:424: bstan pa nyams pa'i dus 'di ru //
NG0605:425: bdud dang dregs pa dgra bgegs rnams //
